title: Maybelline SuperStay Lipcolor ( 16 Hour Color + Conditioning Balm ) 715 Ruby
description: Buy Maybelline Lipsticks - Maybelline SuperStay Lipcolor ( 16 Hour Color + Conditioning Balm ) 715 Ruby. How-to-Use: Apply a thin layer of 16 Hour Color on clean lips.
